  m_text: 'With that in mind, you now have helped Faith organizing boxes to avoid
    getting her belongings inside the boxes getting crushed by the weights.


    And
    as she plans to rehearse soon, you have helped her sort her pages of script by
    prioritization of the higher page number.


    Let''s try and test now your
    skills in organizing through prioritization and structure.


    Take HEAP away!'
